{"submission_id":"sub_a9280e90b0b1d540","run_id":"2026-06-22T19-19-37-798Z_223560-a209711a_ingest_meeting-doc-59341","submitted_at":"2026-06-22T19:24:51.558Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:a9280e90b0b1d540aa0edbb66eb7ba5c030e1e40733867185190712e4978f26a","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_59341","observation_kind":"claim","local_observation_id":"claim_meeting_doc_59341_transformation_plan","label":"Alix Partners Transformation Plan - 6 Significant Changes","raw_text":"The MTA transformation relies on 6 significant changes to the business 1 Refocusing Agency responsibilities on safety, operations and maintenance; including merger of all Bus operations and consideration of separation of Subway and Bus 2 Centralization of Construction & Development function across Agencies and across the lifecycle of capital projects 3 Creation of new central Engineering function to set standards ensuring quality and sustainability of infrastructure 4 Creation of new central Customer Communication function to create clear, high quality, and consistent customer engagement across the MTA 5 Establishment of uniform operating standards as well as the design and optimization of MTA-wide transit network across the entire system and region, rather than agency-by-agency 6 Centralization of all operating support functions, focusing Agencies on service delivery","payload":{"claim_text":"The MTA transformation relies on 6 significant changes to the business: 1 Refocusing Agency responsibilities on safety, operations and maintenance; including merger of all Bus operations and consideration of separation of Subway and Bus. 2 Centralization of Construction & Development function across Agencies and across the lifecycle of capital projects. 3 Creation of new central Engineering function to set standards ensuring quality and sustainability of infrastructure. 4 Creation of new central Customer Communication function to create clear, high quality, and consistent customer engagement across the MTA. 5 Establishment of uniform operating standards as well as the design and optimization of MTA-wide transit network across the entire system and region, rather than agency-by-agency. 6 Centralization of all operating support functions, focusing Agencies on service delivery.","data_type":"transformation_plan","description":"Alix Partners Report recommendations for MTA transformation plan featuring 6 significant changes to business functions.","data_type_normalized":{"raw_text":"transformation_plan","normalized_value":"transformation_plan"}},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_59341","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_59341#p007_c0001","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_59341/blocks.jsonl","page_number":7,"block_id":"p007_c0001","text_sha256":"sha256:fb3873ca852af0b3d436dae0a5b802bb830931dde676ed8cfd4d98bb477361e9","text_source":"raw_text","source_quote":"Alix Partners Report Recommendations"},{"source_id":"meeting_doc_59341","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_59341#p007_c0004","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_59341/blocks.jsonl","page_number":7,"block_id":"p007_c0004","text_sha256":"sha256:bfcab5b1f48304c462730112ef272b1260fcaacfd59d8ee0e36e83754bf612e9","text_source":"raw_text","source_quote":"The MTA transformation relies on 6 significant changes to the business"},{"source_id":"meeting_doc_59341","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_59341#p007_c0005","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_59341/blocks.jsonl","page_number":7,"block_id":"p007_c0005","text_sha256":"sha256:8d1619641cd08ee961b2d36821cdd66886fff2e34a0b2a4effb901334fb0351b","text_source":"raw_text"}]},"validation":{"state":"accepted","issues":[]}}
